defaultLocale.name: Mozilla Archive Format
defaultLocale.description: Save exactly what you see, in a single file. MAFF (based on ZIP) is compact and exceptional for video and audio. MHT (Internet Explorer's format) allows easy exchange with IE users. Store many tabs, find original, and more!

defaultLocale.name: NoScript
defaultLocale.description: Extra protection for your Firefox: NoScript allows JavaScript, Java (and other plugins) only for trusted domains of your choice (e.g. your home-banking web site). This whitelist based pre-emptive blocking approach  prevents exploitation of security vulnerabilities (known and even unknown!) with no loss of functionality... Experts will agree: Firefox is really safer with NoScript :-)
defaultLocale.creator: Giorgio Maone
contributors: Alexander Sokolov and Sergei Smirnov (Russian translation)
Engin Yazılan, Erkan Kaplan & Fathi  (Turkish translation)
X.F Mao & George C. Tsoi (Simplified Chinese)

defaultLocale.name: Classic Theme Restorer
defaultLocale.description: 'Classic Theme Restorer' brings back appmenu button, squared tabs, add-ons bar, small nav-bar buttons, a few older buttons and more to Firefox Australis UI. Use 'Customize' menu to move buttons on toolbars.
defaultLocale.creator: Aris

locales.name: Classic Theme Restorer (Customize Australis)
locales.description: 'Classic Theme Restorer' stellt bekannte Elemente wie die Firefox Menüschaltfläche, quadratische Tabs, Addonleiste, kleine Buttonansicht und einige Buttons wieder her. Über das 'Anpassen'-Menü lassen sich Buttons auf Leisten verschieben.

locales.name: Classic Theme Restorer (Customize Australis)
locales.description: La extensión Classic Theme Restorer restaura menú y botón de la aplicación clásicos, barra de herramientas de complementos, vista de iconos pequeños, botón de menú de marcadores, botones de barras laterales de marcadores e historial, botones pequeños de barra de navegación y pestañas cuadradas, en la interfaz de usuario Australis de Firefox. Use el menú 'Personalizar' para mover botones a su barra de herramientas preferida.

locales.name: Classic Theme Restorer (Customize Australis)
locales.description: Le 'Classic Theme Restorer' add-on restaure appmenu classique, barre d'outils add-ons, bouton de menu des signets, signets bouton de la barre latérale, bouton de barre latérale d'historique, de petits boutons nav-bar et carré onglets sur Firefox Australis UI. Utilisez le menu "Personnaliser" pour déplacer les boutons de votre barre d'outils pratique.

locales.name: Classic Theme Restorer (Customize Australis)
locales.description: 'Classic Theme Restorer' permette di ripristinare il pulsante app, lo stile spigoloso delle schede, la Barra dei componenti aggiuntivi, le icone piccole nella Barra di navigazione, alcuni altri pulsanti presenti nelle versioni precedenti e altri elementi in Australis, la nuova interfaccia di Firefox. Per spostare i pulsanti nelle barre degli strumenti utilizzare il menu Personalizza.

locales.name: Classic Theme Restorer (Customize Australis)
locales.description: «Classic Theme Restorer» возвращает главную кнопку приложения, квадратные вкладки, панель дополнений, маленькие кнопки на панели навигации, несколько старых кнопок и другое, в интерфейсе Australis Firefox. Используйте меню «Настроить», чтобы переместить кнопки на панели инструментов.

defaultLocale.name: Random Agent Spoofer
defaultLocale.description: Allows the use of various browser profiles (including useragent ,platform, oscpu, accept headers and other options), which it can randomly switch between after a chosen period of time has expired
defaultLocale.creator: dbyrne

defaultLocale.name: WorldIP
defaultLocale.description: Professional Geo Add-on with security features and advanced network tools. The real location of web server and extended information about datacenter. Anti-phishing solution. Security features against DNS spoofing and fake websites.
defaultLocale.creator: Alex Aster (Alrond)
